      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·011.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Keang yew sze.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>江有汜，之子歸，不我以，不我以，其後也悔。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Keang has its branches, led from it and returning to it.
Our lady, when she was married,
Would not employ us.
She would not employ us;
But afterwards she repented.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
