      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Keang yew sze.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>江有渚，之子歸，不我與，不我與，其後也處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Keang has its islets.
Our lady, when she was married,
Would not let us be with her.
She would not let us be with her;
But afterwards she repressed [such feelings].</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
