      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Keang yew sze.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>江有沱，之子歸，不我過，不我過，其嘯也歌。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Keang has the T'o.
Our lady, when she was married,
Would not come near us.
She would not come near us;
But she blew that feeling away, and sang.</seg>
      </tuv>
